         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Öthe report of the arouras which he mentionedÖfrom the permissible kinds (sc. of land)Öderelict land in the vicinity of the villages (?) noted below, making it your aim to omit no particulars in these matters and to show no fabvours in taking care of them. Send me the plans of the arouras to be reported, in duplicate, clearly written, having added the measurements and the boundaries, so that the rest may be taken care of in accordance with the instructions. Eirenaios to Horos, greeting. A copy of the letter to Asclepiades is appended. Öaccordingly, and let the plans of the arouras to be reported below be sent to me clearly written. To Asclepiades. TheÖbroughtÖconcerning theÖpermitted to myÖand</ab>
